# Yamato

japanese_yamato_1 = { # Emperor Kinmei
	name = "Hironiwa"

		birth = yes

	535.1.1 = {

		name = "Kin_mei" # Posthumous name
		death = yes
	}
}

	trait = devoted

		birth = yes

		effect ={
			if = {
				limit = { liege_or_court_owner != character:japanese_minamoto_seiwa_10 }
				set_employer = character:japanese_minamoto_seiwa_10 # Yoritomo Minamoto
			}
		}
	}

	}

# Lowborn

japanese_lowborn_1 = {
	name = "Anten"
	faith = mantrayana
	culture = japanese
	trait = loyal
	trait = education_learning_2
	trait = devoted
	830.1.1	 = {
		birth = yes
	}
	867.1.1 = {
		employer = japanese_yamato_181 # Prince Takaoka
		effect = {
			if = {
				limit = { liege_or_court_owner != character:japanese_yamato_181 }
				set_employer = character:japanese_yamato_181 # Prince Takaoka
			}
		}
	}
	881.1.1 = {
		death = yes
	}
}
